<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-32-0818 </DOCNO><TEXT>In connection with energy conservation in Indian industry the articledescribes measures to conserve energy in conveyor systems. Conveyorssystems, especially belt conveyor systems, are the major material handlingsystems in energy-intensive industries as iron and steel, chemical, fertilizer,aluminium, cement and mining industry. A few critical components of abelt conveyor are discussed in connection with investigations to decreasethe energy consumption of the system. (MOS).</TEXT></DOC>